entry.title: TN School Academic Calendar 2023-24 Exam Dates & Holidays
entry.summary: Tamilnadu Schools Academic Calendar 2023-24: Tamil Nadu Education Minister Anbil Mahesh has Released School Calendar for the Next Academic Year i.e., 2023-24. He announced that Schools for 6th to 12 Std will Open on 1st June 2023 after Summer Holidays. More over, Schools for Classes 1st to 5th Std will Reopen on 5th June 2023. The post TN School Academic Calendar 2023-24 Exam Dates & Holidays appeared first on Schools360.in.
